        "title": "Fix nil pointer dereference in auth middleware",
        "body": "## Summary\n\nThis PR fixes a nil pointer dereference that occurred when the auth middleware received a request with a missing or expired context. The fix adds explicit nil checks before dereferencing the context value.\n\n## Changes\n\n- Added nil check for context value in `AuthMiddleware.ServeHTTP`\n- Updated error response to return 401 instead of 500 on missing auth\n- Added unit test covering the nil context case\n\n## Testing\n\nAll existing tests pass. New test added in `auth/middleware_test.go`.",
